Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with image enhancement, which is a common topic in computer vision. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper involves processing of visual media (images) and improving their quality, which falls under the scope of multimedia. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper may be relevant to information retrieval as it deals with improving the quality of images, which can aid in better retrieval of visual information. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper involves processing of images, which is a common topic in computer graphics. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper evaluates the enhanced images based on observer perception, which falls under the scope of human-computer interaction.
